import pandas as pd

def calculate_adosc(df):
    high = df['high']
    low = df['low']
    close = df['close']
    volume = df['volume']
    ad = (close - low - (high - close)) * (high - low)
    adosc = ad * volume
    adosc = adosc.rolling(window=14).mean()
    return adosc
